              <p class="descTitle">Get your business listed</p>
              <p class="bodyTitle">Using the inquiry form on the website</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="middle">
          <div id="borderdColumn">
            <div id="whiteBkg">
              <span class="idContent">2</span>
              <p class="descTitle">We'll help you grow</p>
              <p class="bodyTitle">Offering you an excellent booking system</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <aside id="sidebar">
          <div id="borderdColumn">
            <div id="whiteBkg">
              <span class="idContent">3</span>
              <p class="descTitle">Track your business</p>
              <p class="bodyTitle">Get insights on your performance</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <div class="contentInContent">
          <p class="contentTitle">Join us</p>
          <hr class="titleUnderline">
          <p>We know that you're busy running your business. That's why Stylinger is designed to help you receive and manage more bookings, so you'll grow along with us. We want your customers to feel they get the best out of your services.</p>
          <p>List your business now, or read more about our product.</p>
          <br>
          <a href="#" /><input id="searchBtn" type="submit" value="Get listed" /></a>
          <a href="#" /><input id="searchBtn" type="submit" value="Read more" /></a>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rowContentThird">
        <p class="headerHomeSlanted2">Meet the Team</p>
        <section class="towColL">
